  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86A87bWy6gMY1BVvf17eZG8zibpnj4vVVj0rMu1KsfiazicofqaDrX8PAkDA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505153958\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae94627b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86A87bWy6gMY1BVvf17eZG8zibpnj4vVVj0rMu1KsfiazicofqaDrX8PAkDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">亚马逊的招聘广告正刷爆全网。25万个新岗位、经济复苏、人类与机器的共赢等等词条层出不穷。可就在同一周，一份泄露文件显示，一批AI机器人正在取代超过60万个岗位。外面是热闹的招工现场，里面是机器的冷光闪烁。在效率成为信仰的时代，连「自动化」这个词，都被悄悄改名。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个时代最有戏剧性的两类新闻，竟在同一天出现：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一则写着「亚马逊将在美国扩招25万人」；另一则写着「亚马逊计划让机器人取代60万个岗位」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">前者出现在新闻发布会上，后者藏在泄露文件里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「招人」与「裁人」也只是计算出的结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而亚马逊，是最先写出这段代码的那一个。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153961\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2346368715083799\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"895\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"895\" data-height=\"210\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"132\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=899ff995&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AAbHiayWMv7CM3Siak8dKMAdGCzqrLEqfFguYBqml3L2hT0aSNdmzXqKQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">亚马逊的双重剧本：扩招与解聘</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在几天前，亚马逊高调宣布：今年假日季将在美国扩招25万人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">新闻稿洋溢着乐观的词汇：就业机会、经济复苏、新岗位遍地开花。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但纽约时报拿到的一份泄露文件，暴露了另一面：亚马逊正计划让机器人取代超60万个岗位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这份文件显示，到2033年，公司希望在美国实现75%的运营自动化，在销量翻倍的情况下，无需新增人力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甚至在2027年前，亚马逊就能节省约16万个岗位的雇佣需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不是传统意义的裁员，而是一种「未来式消失」——就好像那些岗位从未存在过。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在亚马逊的仓库里，如今已有超过一百万台机器人参与工作，从早期的搬运系统Kiva，到如今能双脚行走、弯腰取货的Digit，人类的身影正在被算法和机械臂取代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153964\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"720\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6630e3f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AShLBricYWMLvqoMCslzKs2reoic7Studiccl3RphQibaYzNwxvUVRyXneg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">公司高管甚至称这些机器人为「劳动力的未来」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对企业来说，这是效率的胜利；对工人来说，却意味着，连被裁掉的资格都没有。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更现实的是，这场自动化革命将让亚马逊在每件商品上节省约0.3美元的成本，三年累计节约126亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">机器人的算法里没有悲伤，只有利润率的提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153965\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"853\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c600f62d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AvkQOpicCgQJ8gibTew7CPu5l1ZTlrsz0iceHichojEvPyPibqYawibF4re8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">诺贝尔经济学奖得主Daron Acemoglu采访时就说过：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一旦亚马逊找到了盈利的自动化方式，其他公司都会跟上。到那时，美国最大的雇主，也将变成最大的「岗位削减者」。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">于是，外界看到的，是「招聘广告」刷屏；而内部文件里，写着的是「人类冗余」的倒计时。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊，正在用「就业繁荣」的叙事手段，掩饰一场机器革命的本质。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">「AI」成了禁词：亚马逊的语言漂白术</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在文件里，还有一段更微妙的指令。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊的公关团队要求：内部沟通时，尽量不要使用「automation（自动化）」「AI（人工智能）」等词汇，以免引发公众焦虑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">取而代之的，是「advanced technology（先进技术）」「cobot（协作机器人）」这些听起来更温柔的说法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因为在他们看来，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">语言能决定恐惧的温度</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI意味着取代，自动化听起来像失业，而协作机器人，则像人与机器的共同进步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153962\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.561377245508982\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"668\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"668\" data-height=\"375\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"315\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aad23bd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AXlW4FENnm5NsibKsFYk49E9v1MSBhYGO3Ee2FjWibhAial7ic8CEavZ7dg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据多家媒体核实，这类措辞并非偶然。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊的「企业传播与社区关系团队」还提出，未来应通过社区公益项目、员工培训计划等方式，改善公众对技术替代的情绪认知。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这家公司并不打算停止自动化，只是想让自动化听起来没那么可怕。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是无疑是一场语言层面的公关战。当AI被称「先进技术」，裁员被包装成「效率优化」，机器的进入就不再刺眼，人类的退出，也显得不再悲伤。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153963\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5810147299509002\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"611\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"611\" data-height=\"355\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"327\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c89d2b45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86A7diaCPEzSu499b4n1QxB7rkQj1PcSscOkBibszNcibfOWBAdcJThryE2w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">面对外界质疑，亚马逊发言人Kelly Nantel在采访时回应：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0px 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些泄露文件只代表某个团队的视角，并不反映公司的整体招聘策略。我们仍在积极招聘，并计划在全国范围内新增25万个岗位。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从公关角度看，这段回应几乎完美地印证了文件中的思路——不否认自动化，只是换了一种更体面的语言去描述它。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">于是，自动化首先取代的，并不是人类工人，而是「自动化」这个词本身。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">省下30美分，却丢掉60万份工作</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当你在亚马逊上点下「下单」按钮的那一刻，一个看不见的计算开始运转。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊预估，借助机器人与自动化系统，每件商品可节省约0.3美元成本，从2025年至2027年可累计节省126亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">到2032年，机器人自动化每年将为亚马逊节约160亿美元的运营成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这组数字揭示了一个残酷的逻辑：当一件商品能节省0.3 美元，当机器人替代岗位、提升效率成为可量化目标，那么劳动、时间、甚至人本身的价值便开始被边缘化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153966\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48583333333333334\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"583\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"273\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb45accb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AaEB6v7xKzJDbHib67fOcnNZibJkbicDumnSiczR2XoOUvMvMRMuOgkkBHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从企业的角度出发，这是利润率的必然选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但从劳工与社会维度观察，这意味着人类的劳动正被算法转化为零碎的成本变量。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当亚马逊的自动化占比上升，一件原本包含数十分钟人工的包裹，可能只需要数分钟机器人操作。节省的不是机器人的电费，而是，人类「动手做事」的权限。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当更便宜、更快、更高效成为零售世界的新标准，价格和工作的尊严可能被一并压缩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">美国工会联合会近年的报告指出，仓储自动化正成为新一轮结构性失业的源头，尤其在中低学历人群中，替代效应愈发明显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153968\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3101265822784811\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"474\" style=\"width:338px;height:443px;\" data-width=\"474\" data-height=\"621\" data-backw=\"474\" data-backh=\"621\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ed55963&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AAUqib4ibs20PDbK0ZC5h008wNQoWrWgDMBZSU7x6509YlSr45f3wcbmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">便宜的代价，不再只是货品的价格，而是社会整体的劳动安全网。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">无人仓库之后，是无人社会</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">物流仓库只是起点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在亚马逊的实验里，机器人负责拣货、打包、贴签；算法规划动线；程序预测需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当所有环节都能被预测、被取代、被优化时，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「人」就成了系统里最不稳定的变量</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而这场自动化革命的余震，正在从仓库向更广的世界蔓延。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">美国劳工统计局数据显示，仓储与配送是近十年增长最快的蓝领岗位之一，吸纳了大量中低收入劳动者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但一旦亚马逊的自动化路径被证明可盈利，它就会成为整个行业的模板。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">物流公司、制造企业、甚至零售终端都会跟进。到那时，消失的不是60万个岗位，而是一整类工作形态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505153969\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"5000\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"5000\" data-height=\"3333\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c715566e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86Arsok6NVzh5eDJJkbeLt2OHyGoico5LR2H9icwmJxthFCiaA3icNibM0DBFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经济学家Daron Acemoglu警告：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">没有任何一家企业比亚马逊更有动力去找到自动化的盈利方式。一旦它成功，这种趋势将扩散到各个行业。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，一旦自动化成为主流逻辑，劳动市场不再以人为中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">算法根据效率配置资源，资本根据收益分配权力，社会正在悄悄完成一次「去人化」的重组。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更微妙的，是消费者的变化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们享受着更快的物流、更低的价格，却也在用每一次点击投票，默许人类劳动被削减的过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「更便宜」与「更公正」，站在了对立面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这个体系里，机器不会疲惫，也不会抗议。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们只会执行命令，直到世界也变得和它们一样：高效、冷静、精准，却越来越无人化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">亚马逊只是先行者。在它之后，无数公司都在学习同一套算法：如何「优化掉人」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从仓库出发，自动化正沿着供应链一路向外蔓延，最终抵达每一个被效率驯化的角落。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">机器的世界越来越亮，而人类的存在，正在从舞台中央退到光影之间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也许未来没有「失业」。只是，我们都被安置在了系统之外。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/news/803257/amazon-robotics-automation-replace-600000-human-jobs\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/news/803257/amazon-robotics-automation-replace-600000-human-jobs</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://gizmodo.com/leaked-amazon-plans-say-robots-will-help-it-avoid-hiring-600000-workers-2000674920?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://gizmodo.com/leaked-amazon-plans-say-robots-will-help-it-avoid-hiring-600000-workers-2000674920?utm_source=chatgpt.com</a></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "亚马逊通过机器人大军三年内节省 126 亿美元，计划取代超 60 万岗位，同时用“语言漂白术”掩饰自动化对就业的深远影响。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "亚马逊通过机器人大军三年内节省 126 亿美元，计划取代超 60 万岗位，同时用“语言漂白术”掩饰自动化对就业的深远影响。",
  "summary": "文章揭露了亚马逊在公开宣布扩招 25 万人的同时，一份泄露文件显示其计划到 2033 年实现 75%的运营自动化，从而取代超过 60 万个岗位，并预计在 2025-2027 年累计节省 126 亿美元。文章深入分析了亚马逊通过“先进技术”、“协作机器人”等词汇替代“自动化”和“AI”的“语言漂白术”，旨在避免公众对大规模技术替代的焦虑。作者指出，这种效率至上的自动化趋势不仅在亚马逊仓库蔓延，更预示着未来劳动力市场“去人化”的结构性变革，可能导致中低学历人群的结构性失业，引发了对就业结构、社会公平和消费者选择的深刻反思，并警告这种模式将扩散至其他行业。",
